name: Brian
message: This is Thomas Jones in NY. You and I are scheduled to do a field audit on 6/23. Please meet me at the OndeiAN at 8:00am in front of the main lobby desk. Please bring your contracts, planogram, chain authorization forms. Please confirm via octel that you have received this message. If you need to contact me, I can be reached at 212-878-2296. I look forward to working with you on 6/23.
